Forever valentines 💌 
ITS OFFICIAL 💗
Guess all the rumours are true !
Every day together feels like valentine’s. We are beyond grateful for our hearts to start on this brand new journey ahead, crazy in love and sane in life. We can’t wait for all the memories we’ll create and share it with you guys. Here’s to love, laughter, and a lifetime of happiness. 
WE CANT WAIT TO CELEBRATE WITH YALL.❤️
